g="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Mantra-of-The-Cosmos-press-photo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><div><p> <a href="/artists/mantra-of-the-cosmos">Mantra Of The Cosmos——</a>由肖恩·莱德（《<a href="/artists/happy-mondays">快乐星期一》</a> 、 <a href="/artists/black-grape">《黑葡萄</a>》）、鼓手扎克·斯塔基（ <a href="/artists/the-who">《谁人</a>》、《<a href="/aritsts/oasis">绿洲</a>》）、吉他手安迪·贝尔（《<a href="/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>》、 <a href="/artists/ride">《骑行</a>》）和贝兹（《<a href="/artists/happy-mondays">星期一快乐</a>》、 <a href="/artists/black-grape">《黑葡萄</a>》）组成的新乐队——分享了他们的作品新单曲“X (Wot You Sayin?)”并向<em>NME</em>谈论了他们即将推出的计划。</p><p>该团体是由林戈·斯塔尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">(Ringo Starr)</a>的儿子斯塔基 (Starkey) 组建的，他最初在疫情期间尝试与前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kraftwerk">Kraftwerk</a>成员卡尔·巴托斯 (Karl Bartos) 合作开展德国泡菜摇滚项目。</p><p> “我想让他制作这首歌并写歌词，因为我真的很喜欢他的独奏作品以及他与 Kraftwerk 所做的事情，”斯塔基通过 Zoom 告诉<em>NME</em> 。他煞费苦心地指出 Mantra 并不是一个超级团体。 “他的言论非常疯狂，而且他能够跳出框框思考。所以我试着给他打电话，他[采用德国口音]说，“你应该在十年前给我打电话，当时我还年轻，可以做到这一点。”所以我把它搁置了。</p><p> “两年后，我再次思考这个问题，暗示我应该组建一个超级组合。我说，‘你知道超级群是什么意思吗？这意味着四个人正在手淫。这不是很诚实的音乐。这与言语无关。我以为唯一能创作这种迷幻诗歌的人——不是愚蠢的吉他连复段——是肖恩。所以我拿到了他的电话号码，给他打电话，说了我现在对你说的话，肖恩说，‘我他妈的在地狱里’。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="宇宙咒语 - X（你说啥？）（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bB0XPr13RvI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该团体已经发行了令人震惊的电子单曲“Gorilla Guerilla”，并最近在格拉斯顿伯里表演。随着他们迷幻的新单曲的发行，我们采访了 Starkey 和 Ryder，讨论了他们的专辑计划、林戈的建议、他们对人工智能的想法以及绿洲重聚。</p><h2> <strong>NME：肖恩，你说过 Mantra Of The Cosmos 听起来和你的其他乐队一点都不像。这是故意的吗？</strong></h2><p> <strong>Shaun</strong> ：“嗯，是的，当你想到我们所做的一切时，即使是在星期一，[我们的首张专辑]《Squirrel And G-Man》对我来说距离《Bummed》至少有 110 英里，这是一个很好的选择。”距离他妈的“Pills &#39;N&#39; Thrills”有 500 英里，然后我们有了最后一张 [“Yes Please！”] 这应该是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-grape">Black Grape 的</a>第一张专辑，但我们以另一种方式结束了。这支乐队也是一样，但又有不同。”</p><h2><strong>到目前为止，双方的合作情况如何？</strong></h2><p><strong>肖恩</strong>：“是的，太棒了。我喜欢它，因为我们彼此都很陌生，我们仍然和乐队一起去录音室，穿上旧乐队舒适的拖鞋，我和和我一起工作的人感觉很好。扎克（Zak）是让我们的节奏融合在一起的人，然后我进来添加人声，安迪（Andy）添加他的吉他。对我来说，你可以说[采用冷漠的时髦口音]这是“庄严的，有点实验性，但实际上这就是正在发生的事情”。不，这真的很放松，你明白我的意思吗？当你制作音乐时，可能会很肛门，但对我们来说，我们基本上做我们想做的事。扎克把这一切都记录下来，然后乱搞。” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_mantraofthecosmos_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Mantra Of The Cosmos 乐队的 Bez、Zak Starkey、Shaun Ryder 和 Andy Bell 于 2023 年 6 月 5 日在伦敦 The Box 演出前在后台摆姿势，图片来源：Dave Benett/Getty Images</figcaption></figure></div><h2><strong>到目前为止你已经录制了很多歌曲吗？</strong></h2><div><p> <strong>Zak</strong> （笑）：“是的，大约 175。”</p><p><strong>肖恩</strong>：“我们有很多材料。如果你想要一些可以持续两分半或三分钟的歌曲（笑），那么我估计我们有大约 175 首歌曲，不是吗？或者我们可以播放一些<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">平克</a>·弗洛伊德风格的音乐，每个音乐持续 35 分钟。这只是取决于扎克会把它变成什么样子。这就是它的有趣之处。我有时会离开工作室，回来后我会在里面放一些东西，但扎克只是将它混合成不同的东西。他挑选了我要推出的东西，我只是想让他们脸上露出微笑并享受它。</p></div><h2><strong>这些歌曲是关于什么的？</strong></h2><div><p><strong>肖恩</strong>：“他们有点像我，真的，毫无意义的胡言乱语。你知道，疯狂的、破碎的卡通人物[再次采用时髦的口音]“在不同维度的褪色的古怪世界中，我什至不知道自己到底在说什么”。不，说实话，我写歌的方式，说实话，是很自私的。我写它们是为了让自己发笑，我写它们是为了让其他人……当他们把这些歌词放在一起时，它们对他们来说可能意味着一些东西。在我这个年纪，我现在花了很多时间在他妈的过去上，我只会继续说30年前说过的话。所以这确实是连环漫画黑色喜剧，完全是胡说八道。”</p><p><strong>扎克</strong>：“肖恩（在工作室）会做四个镜头，当我编辑它们时，每个镜头都是相互关联的，无论是困扰他还是他脑子里想到的东西，都会出来。顺序不一定正确，但一切正常。所以这并不是一项非常困难的工作。”</p></div><h2><strong>您最近演奏了格拉斯顿伯里音乐节。怎么样？</strong></h2><div><p><strong>肖恩</strong>：“我们和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink-floyd">埃尔顿·约翰</a>同时在场。你在格拉斯顿伯里他妈的埃尔顿一定会得到多么美妙的演出，对吧？我们可能会想：“[我们的演出]那里会他妈的吗？”但这只是表明有多少奇怪的、小怪异的人准备来观看我们的乐队。”</p><p> <strong>Zak</strong> ：“当我们开始时，Glade 舞台上已经挤满了人。当我们完成时它已经很满了。我们的对手们都非常努力地挖掘它。没有人走开去观看埃尔顿，因为我们正在为已经吸毒四天的人播放催眠音乐。你还能要求什么呢？”</p></div><h2><strong>扎克，我相信你爸爸听过《宇宙咒语》的材料吧？</strong></h2><div><p><strong>扎克</strong>：“是的，他都听过，而且他真的很喜欢。他爱肖恩，也喜欢他所唱的内容。一首歌曲中有一句歌词叫“Belly Full Of Lard”，他说他已经有 40 或 50 年没有听过类似的歌了。还有一封信是这样写的： <em>“我在国民医疗服务体系（NHS）找到了一份工作，它改变了我的生活”，</em>而我父亲则大声喊道“他妈的一团糟”。他以前从未听过这句话，却把这句话钉牢了。他已经受够了，伙计，他真的受够了。” </p></div><div><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Ringo-Starr-Peace-Love.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">林戈·斯塔尔 图片来源：Getty</figcaption></figure></div><h2><strong>您对人工智能作曲有何看法？</strong></h2><div><div><p><strong>扎克</strong>：[笑]“我想知道它是否可以帮我写一些你的歌词，肖恩？</p><p><strong>肖恩</strong>：“哈，是的。很疯狂的是，现在有一个（计算机）程序，你可以说，“给我写一首像肖恩·莱德那样的歌曲”，人工智能就会给你写一首像肖恩·莱德那样的歌曲。不过，你必须聪明地使用它。如果你很糟糕，你可以使用它，但如果你聪明并且使用它，那就会成为一种技能，就会成为一种艺术形式，而那些聪明的人就会创造出新的、不同的东西。不过，你不会取代音乐家。那不会发生。但了解自己游戏的人（会用它做点什么）。”</p></div></div><div><h2><strong>肖恩，你现在60岁了。你有没有想过在这个年纪你还会继续创作音乐？</strong></h2><div><strong>肖恩</strong>：“这就是我们的目标，是的。一旦我进入游戏，我就想，我哪儿也不去；我要去哪里？我不会他妈的收拾好一切并试图找到一份工作，因为无论如何我都找不到工作。我无法融入那个世界；我从没干过。所以当我们做音乐和乐队的时候，我和贝兹不只是在那里搞砸。我们知道我们的面包是在哪里涂黄油的。”</div><h2><strong>扎克，你曾经来过绿洲。你认为他们会复合吗？</strong></h2><div><p><strong>肖恩</strong>：“不，还没有。”</p><p><strong>扎克</strong>：“我现在不这么认为。我认为每个人都像他们一样幸福。利亚姆做得很好。他非常勇敢地邀请了这些作家，并把自己的自负抛在了一边。诺埃尔仍然在创作伟大的音乐。”</p></div></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shaun-ryder-and-zak-starkey-on-mantra-of-the-cosmos-do-you-know-what-a-supergroup-means-four-guys-having-a-wank-3480446">肖恩·莱德 (Shaun Ryder) 和扎克·斯塔基 (Zak Starkey) 在 Mantra Of The Cosmos 上发表的帖子：“你知道超级群体是什么意思吗？四个家伙手淫”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
国际刑警组织和丹尼尔·艾弗里谈“插值”：“我们试图找到不拘一格的东西” https://www.nme.com/news/music/interpol-and-daniel-avery-on-interpolations-we-were-trying-to-find-something-electic-3483453?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=interpol-丹尼尔·艾利谈插值法，我们试图找到折衷的东西Anagricel DuranWed, 16 Aug 2023 12:59:11 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3483453 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="国际刑警组织。图片来源：Ebru Yildiz" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在这里查看该项目的最终曲目，国际刑警组织的 Daniel Kessler 和 Daniel Avery 讨论“Interpolations”的创作</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/interpol-and-daniel-avery-on-interpolations-we-were-trying-to-find-something-eclectic-3483453">国际刑警组织和丹尼尔·艾弗里关于“插值”的帖子：“我们试图找到不拘一格的东西”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="国际刑警组织。图片来源：Ebru Yildiz" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Interpol.-Credit_-Credit_-Ebru-Yildiz-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/interpol">国际刑警</a>组织与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-avery">Daniel Avery</a>合作，为他们的“Interpolations”项目的最后部分创建了一个精简版的“格林威治”。请查看下面的内容以及我们的采访和合作。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/interpol-new-album-the-other-side-of-make-believe-interview-3266415">国际刑警组织：“我们被所有唱片公司拒绝——包括我们签约的唱片公司”</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 4 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/interpol-share-new-documentary-and-announce-remix-project-with-daniel-avery-makaya-mccraven-and-more-3432644">国际刑警组织就宣布推出“Interpolations</a> ”——这是一个合作系列，由五位不同的艺术家重新创作了乐队 2022 年 LP“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/interpol-the-other-side-of-make-believe-album-review-3267584">The Other Side Of Make Believe</a> ”中的精选曲目。</p><p>每月发布一次，第一首分享的曲目是 Makaya McCraven 的重新想象版“Big Shot City”，随后是 Jeff Parker 版本的“Passenger”、Jesu 版本的“Toni”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/WATER-FROM-YOUR-EYES">Water From Your Eyes</a>版本的“有些事情改变了”。</p><p>今天，乐队与 DJ 兼制作人 Daniel Avery 合作，发布了《Interpolations》的最后一首歌曲。</p><p> “可以毫不夸张地说，国际刑警组织的音乐帮助塑造了我年轻时的生活，因此我非常自豪地为《格林威治》呈现这个混音版，”艾弗里在一份声明中说道。 “一开始我不愿意接触这首歌，但我觉得我已经找到了我自己版本的乐队诱人的影子，这对我来说一直意义重大。”</p><p> <em>NME</em>采访了制作人兼国际刑警组织吉他手 Daniel Kessler，讨论了该项目的创作、Avery 的修改过程以及两位音乐家目前的工作。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="格林威治（丹尼尔·艾弗里插值）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DCIrpNo6Awg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3><strong>新医学经济学。你好。 “插值”的想法从何而来？</strong></h3><p><strong>凯斯勒</strong>：“这是与我们的唱片公司 Matador 进行的一次讨论，讨论我们可以做但我们还没有真正做太多的事情。这个想法[“插值”]是在谈话中提出的，然后，正如丹尼尔[艾弗里]可能记得的那样，近十年来我一直在催促他对我们的一首曲目进行混音，所以当丹尼尔这样做时我真的很兴奋‘格林威治’。”</p><h3><strong>选择最终参与该项目的五位艺术家的过程是怎样的？</strong></h3><p><strong>凯斯勒：</strong> “我们希望拥有一系列艺术家，包括我们的粉丝。 Water From Your Eyes 是我们的品牌伙伴。他们也是我们已经一起巡演过几次并成为好朋友的乐队。”</p><p> “我们喜欢他们的音乐，他们也在做自己的事情。你可以从他们的混音中听到这一点，这是对这首歌的独特诠释。还有杰夫·帕克，我永远是他的粉丝。这只是一种真正尝试寻找不拘一格的东西，我喜欢这一切结合在一起的方式。”</p><h3><strong>是每个艺术家都选择了他们想要创作的歌曲，还是你们作为乐队为每个艺术家分配了一首曲目？</strong></h3><p><strong>凯斯勒：</strong> “每位艺术家都会选择他们想要创作的歌曲。我们想给他们选择，让他们选择与重新解释的人交谈的内容。他们可能会听其中一个想法，然后说，‘我有一个想法’，或者‘有些东西在情感上打击了我，我想强调这一点，但可能不那么明显’。”</p><p> “当你能够提供这个机会而不是像‘我们需要这首歌的混音，因为它将成为这首歌的最新单曲’时，这真是太好了。将其作为一项艺术事业来保留是很酷的事情，这就是事实。”</p><h3><strong>艾弗里，为什么国际刑警组织对你如此重要？</strong></h3><p><strong>艾弗里：</strong> “我在人生的一个非常重要的时期发现了国际刑警组织。那一刻，我不仅真的很喜欢磨练自己的音乐品味和唱片收藏，而且我开始进入夜晚，我发现了这个特殊的俱乐部之夜，它真的让我大开眼界，看到了在夜晚的可能性。那个世界。”</p><p> “俱乐部之夜播放了很多有趣的电子音乐，但也播放了很多令人兴奋的吉他音乐，国际刑警组织就在其中。我最终在那个俱乐部之夜得到了一份 DJ 的工作，这就是我一切的开始。国际刑警组织当然为我人生的转折点配乐，所以他们对我来说就像一支特殊的乐队。” </p><figure id="attachment_3483542" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3483542" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3483542" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick.jpg" alt="丹尼尔·艾弗里.图片来源：史蒂夫·古利克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Daniel-Avery.-Credit-Steve-Gullick-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3483542" class="wp-caption-text">丹尼尔·艾弗里.图片来源：史蒂夫·古利克</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>凯斯勒，艾弗里是什么让他非常适合这个项目？</strong></h3><p> <strong>Kessler</strong> ：“我们俩刚刚在 2014 年参加了一个音乐节。一位名叫 Dave 的共同朋友向我们介绍了我们，那天晚上我们就一起出去玩了，气氛非常好。我想就在那天晚上之后，我又回到了[艾弗里的]目录。我认为《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-14847-320692">Drone Logic</a> 》刚刚问世，它就成了我的配乐。”</p><p> “我们发行了《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-interpol-15588-325570">El Pintor</a> 》，无论我们走到哪里，这张唱片都会一直重复播放。在那之后，我就像“我想让丹尼尔混音我们的一首曲目”，然后就变成了寻找适合丹尼尔的时间。能有这样的机会真是太棒了。”</p><h3><strong>艾弗里，你是如何在尊重歌曲起源的同时，对一支在你的生活中发挥重要作用的乐队的歌曲进行修改的？</strong></h3><p><strong>艾弗里：</strong> “老实说，我的恐惧很大一部分原因是我害怕接触一支对我来说意义重大的乐队。但是，这个项目成功了，而且时间安排也很完美，我想，‘让我们尝试一下吧’。”</p><p> “当有如此多的选择时，很难确切地知道该选择什么，但‘格林威治’有一些东西。我听到了其中的一些内容，我想也许我可以使用我的工具通过自己的镜头进行拍摄和过滤。我不想只是做一个加强版本，但我也不想只是制作一首与原版毫无相似之处的俱乐部曲目。”</p><p> “结果确实是介于这些事情中间的东西。我真的很着迷于听到这首歌的人声层次。在我非常喜欢使用的歌曲下面还有一个女声，我认为它带出了歌曲本身的不同方面。 It&#39;s my interpretation of the band. It was difficult to work out what to do, but I&#39;m really happy with what came out.”</p><p> <strong>Kessler</strong> : “I think it sounds amazing. It&#39;s such a pleasure to hear such a different take of this piece of music and then also to take elements that are not completely all on the top of the surface and super obvious but take something and make a motif out of it as Daniel did on on this mix of &#39;Greenwich&#39;, it&#39;s just like a really different approach to the whole composition.”</p><p> <strong>Avery:</strong> “One of the things I have always loved about Interpol as band is that there&#39;s a real broken beauty to everything they do. It&#39;s equally sad, and uplifting. And in the same way, I wanted to make something that was heavy, but I thought still had enough sort of light in there somewhere. That&#39;s what I mean when I say that&#39;s my interpretation of the band.” </p><figure id="attachment_3432647" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3432647" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3432647" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000.jpg" alt="Interpol, 2022. Credit: Ebru Yildiz" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/INTERPOL_Ebru-Yildiz_2000-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3432647" class="wp-caption-text"> Interpol, 2022. Credit: Ebru Yildiz</figcaption></figure><h3> <strong>Avery, your last release was a compilation of B-sides called &#39;More Truth&#39; – is there anything you&#39;re working on at the moment that will be out soon?</strong></h3><p> <strong>Avery:</strong> I am working on a lot of new stuff at the moment. Release wise. Still, yet to be determined. There&#39;s a lot happening at the moment so more news soon.</p><h3> <strong>Interpol played <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/interpol-play-antics-in-full-paris-show-watch-footage-setlist-3465741">&#39;Antics&#39; in its entirety in Paris</a> back in July and just recently played <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/interpol-play-turn-on-the-bright-lights-in-full-outside-lands-21st-anniversary-3482616">&#39;Turn On The Bright Lights&#39; in its entirety a few days ago at Outside Lands</a> . How has it been revisiting these albums again?</strong></h3><p> <strong>Kessler:</strong> “Yeah, it&#39;s great. It was challenging. We are touring festival season, where you don&#39;t get soundchecks and you don&#39;t get much performance time. You want to do the records justice. Also, you make these records and you put them in a listening order. Performance orders are a very different vibe.”</p><p> “So it&#39;s really something that you have to prepare yourself to do. You have to relearn how to play the song&#39;s that you haven&#39;t played in a while. You also don&#39;t want to just do a 50 per cent version of it, you want to make it as good as people want to hear it. I think it puts you on the right kind of level of nerves where you want to do it justice, but you&#39;re also present in the moment. And it&#39;s exhilarating. It&#39;s also nice that people even care about something that you created that long ago. I feel very honoured and grateful that people do. It was great to play and revisit those albums.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Interpol - &quot;Big Shot City (Makaya McCraven Interpolation)&quot; (Official Audio)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kWpGT4Prc6Y?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Interpol are currently on tour in North America with <a href="/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">The Smashing Pumpkins</a> up until September 9. <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Finterpol-tickets%2Fartist%2F836507" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> for any remaining tickets.</p><p> They have also recently announced a handful of headlining gigs kicking off with a show at the House of Blues in Anaheim, California in October and two headlining shows at New York City&#39;s Beacon Theatre in December. Tickets are set to go on sale this Friday, August 18. <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Finterpol-tickets%2Fartist%2F836507" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit here</a> to purchase tickets.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/interpol-and-daniel-avery-on-interpolations-we-were-trying-to-find-something-eclectic-3483453">Interpol and Daniel Avery on &#39;Interpolations&#39;: “We were trying to find something eclectic”</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 Megadeth crossovers announced for 'World Of Tanks' and 'World Of Warships' https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/megadeth-crossovers-announced-for-world-of-tanks-and-world-of-warships-3483812?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=megadeth-crossovers-announced-for-world-of-tanks-and-world-of-warshipsImogen Donovan Wed, 16 Aug 2023 12:38:08 +0000 Gaming NewsMusic NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3483812 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Starting on August 29</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/megadeth-crossovers-announced-for-world-of-tanks-and-world-of-warships-3483812">Megadeth crossovers announced for &#39;World Of Tanks&#39; and &#39;World Of Warships&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/wargaming-megadeth-festival-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/wargaming">Wargaming</a> has revealed that the iconic metal band <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megadeth">Megadeth</a> will be headlining the upcoming <a href="https://megadeth.wargaming.net/">Wargaming Metal Fest</a> for the <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/games/world-of-tanks">World Of Tanks</a></em> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/games/world-of-warships"><em>World Of Warships</em></a> community.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/its-a-golden-age-for-music-collaborations-in-gaming-3383562">It&#39;s a golden age for music collaborations in gaming</a></strong></li></ul><p> Vic Rattlehead – Megadeth&#39;s mascot – will also appear for the first time in a video game. As a fully fleshed out character, Vic will be one of the voiceovers that players will hear in the Metal Fest, alongside frontman Dave Mustaine, guitarist Kiko Loureiro, bassist James Lomenzo and drummer Dirk Verbeuren.</p><p> Specifically speaking, Metal Fest will be held in <em>World of Tanks Blitz, World of Tanks Modern Armor, World of Warships</em> and <em>World of Warships: Legends</em> . The event will begin on August 29 and end on October 3, offering players plenty of time to accrue and “array of Megadeth-branded in-game items such as tanks and warships, in-game missions and quests, integrated songs, and much more”.</p><p> “This is the first time our images have been immortalised in video games! Moreover, our mascot has unleashed its own roaring voice, adding even more metal mayhem to the games,” said Mustaine. In both his <em>World Of Tanks</em> and <em>World Of Warships</em> versions, Vic has his recognisable steel visor, ear caps and vice clamping his teeth shut, though the uniforms are different. </p><figure id="attachment_3353455" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3353455" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3353455" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011.jpg" alt="Megadeth's Dave Mustaine" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Dave-Mustaine-Megadeth-2011-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3353455" class="wp-caption-text"> Megadeth&#39;s Dave Mustaine performs during Sonisphere Festival in the UK in 2011. Credit: Jim Dyson/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “We&#39;ve laid down over 350 mind-melting voice lines, and players will feel the thunder as we command during the battles. We have tanks, we have warships, and we are ready for Wargaming Metal Fest!” concluded Mustaine.</p><p> Earlier this year, Megadeth once again made headlines after <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-drummer-dirk-verbeuren-the-killers-mr-brightside-3469205">Verbeuren replicated The Killers&#39; &#39;Mr. Brightside&#39; on the drums after hearing the track for the first time</a> .</p><p> After listening to the original version, Verbeuren said: “Badass. I have to say, I can see why it&#39;s a classic. It&#39;s a killer song. I can totally see how that would rule on stage and people would go crazy. Great drum parts, very well balanced.”</p><p> In other gaming news, Netflix Games will <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/netflix-games-to-support-four-new-studios-through-black-voices-in-gaming-nonprofit-3483351">support four new studios over the next three months</a> through the Black Voices in Gaming nonprofit.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/megadeth-crossovers-announced-for-world-of-tanks-and-world-of-warships-3483812">Megadeth crossovers announced for &#39;World Of Tanks&#39; and &#39;World Of Warships&#39;</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
 'Warrior Nun' fans react to show's return as new film trilogy https://www.nme.com/news/tv/warrior-nun-fans-react-to-shows-return-as-new-film-trilogy-3483810?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=warrior-nun-fans-react-to-shows-return-as-new-film-trilogyHollie Geraghty Wed, 16 Aug 2023 12:27:07 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflix https://www.nme.com/?p=3483810 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> &quot;I could never dream so big&quot;</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/warrior-nun-fans-react-to-shows-return-as-new-film-trilogy-3483810">&#39;Warrior Nun&#39; fans react to show&#39;s return as new film trilogy</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/warrior-nun-trilogy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Fans have reacted to the news that the popular <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a> fantasy series <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/warrior-nun"><em>Warrior Nun</em></a> will be returning as a film trilogy.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/warrior-nun-campagin-netflix-cancelled-billboard-alba-baptista-3389279">Why is &#39;Warrior Nun&#39; the most-talked about TV show on the internet?</a></strong></li></ul><p> The show is based on the comic series by Ben Dunn and follows Ava Silva (Alba Baptista), who is resurrected by a divine artifact in her back before discovering she has supernatural powers and is part of an ancient order tasked with fighting demons on Earth.</p><p> Shortly after the release of <em>Warrior Nun</em> season two, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/warrior-nun-season-two-highest-netflix-audience-rating-ever-3355909">it was reported to have the highest Netflix audience rating ever</a> . Netflix, however, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/warrior-nun-cancelled-netflix-two-seasons-3366663">cancelled the show after two seasons back in December 2022</a> .</p><p> The cancellation sparked a lengthy fan campaign to resurrect the show, with one of the campaigning tactics including <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/warrior-nun-fans-buy-billboard-outside-netflix-headquarters-asking-for-a-third-season-3384617">renting a billboard outside of Netflix&#39;s Los Angeles headquarters</a> .</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/warrior-nun-creator-confirms-netflix-show-will-return-3462345">Creator Simon Barry</a> then confirmed in June that it “will return” and would be “more EPIC than you could imagine”. </p><figure id="attachment_3462350" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3462350" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3462350" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270.jpg" alt="武士修女" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/warrior-nun@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3462350" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Warrior Nun&#39;. Credit: Netflix</figcaption></figure><p> Now, executive producer Dean English has announced that <em>Warrior Nun</em> will be returning as three films.</p><p> “I need to start by thanking all of you loyal fans,” he said in a video <a href="https://www.warriornunsaved.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">statement</a> shared on Tuesday (August 15). “Because of you and your incredible energy that we keep pushing forward to make these stories. You guys really make it all worthwhile. So thank you so much for your continued support.”</p><p> Announcing that <em>Warrior Nun</em> is set to return in the form of a movie trilogy, he said: “One thing we need to touch on involves the strike in Hollywood involving actors and writers.因此，我们今天无法在这方面发布任何公告。</p><p> “Some may ask, “Does this perhaps infer that there&#39;s going to be a universe being launched of Warrior Nun, which could expand into films and TV series following characters that we already know?”这个问题的答案是肯定的。 And there will be more details in the future.” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="武士修女获救 8 月 15 日公告" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zgAUSCdj42w?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> English encouraged fans to sign up for a mailing list to receive exclusive updates, concluding: “I want to say that you guys have made me very, very proud through all your hard work and inspired me all the time to keep going. So in this life or the next.”</p><p> Fans have been expressing their excitement and delight at the news on social media, with many changing the original #SaveWarriorNun hashtag to #WarriorNunSaved.</p><p> “The news we&#39;ve been waiting for,” one X/Twitter user shared. “Warrior Nun as a movie trilogy!! I could never dream so big!!” another added.</p><p> “I&#39;m sorry, I blacked out, does this really say THREE movies,” a third wrote.</p><p> Check out some more fan reactions below.</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> im sorry, i blacked out, does this really say THREE movies <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/warriornun?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#warriornun</a> <a href="https://t.co/r1m6fmfst3">pic.twitter.com/r1m6fmfst3</a></p><p> — Nora Dominick (@noradominick) <a href="https://twitter.com/noradominick/status/1691617023791341787?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 16, 2023</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> &quot;1 ticket to Warrior nun please&quot; <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/WarriorNunSaved?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#WarriorNunSaved</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/WarriorNun?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#WarriorNun</a> <a href="https://t.co/537xPxYDJk">pic.twitter.com/537xPxYDJk</a></p><p> — Riley <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/